    "body" : "<p>If using maven try putting it in </p>\n\n<pre><code>/src/main/resources\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>If using simple eclipse project (without maven), put it in project root directory (not in the src)\n<img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/kGZeS.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></p>\n\n<p>Also you misspelled the name of the file in the source</p>\n\n<pre><code>return new Configuration().configure(\"hibernate.cgf.xml\").buildSessionFactory();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>it must be </p>\n\n<pre><code>hibernate.cfg.xml\n</code></pre>\n"
